---
description: Security rules
alwaysApply: true
---
- Backend validates everything; frontend validation is UX only.
- Uploads: consent required, one file, size/MIME/extension/magic-byte/decode checks, optional ClamAV (fail closed in prod).
- Images: memory only, zero-fill buffer in finally, never log/persist/return image bytes.
- Secrets backend-only; safe error envelope; helmet+CORS+rate limits on; logs redacted.
